README - BC FTCtW
===============================


What is the BC FTCtW extension?
=============================================

Provides for custom design extension for customer's
BC Event Filter Group Calendaring Solution.

eZ Network Guidelines label this extension as type 'A'.


Version
=======

The current version of BC FTCtW is 1.0.1.
Last Updated: February 14, 2008

You can find details about changes for this
version in doc/changelogs/CHANGELOG-1.0.1


